OL,3,CMorrison and Swann settle legal case
OL,5,FSir Van Morrison's long-running
OL,6,Fdefamation battle with former Stormont
OL,7,FHealth Minister Robin Swann has been
OL,8,Fsettled, the High Court heard today.
OL,10,FConfidential resolutions were reached
OL,11,Fin their competing and "potentially
OL,12,Fvery costly" lawsuits over the
OL,13,Fhandling of Covid restrictions in
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland, a judge was told.
OL,16,FThe outcome followed a successful
OL,17,Fmediation process ahead of planned
OL,18,Fjury trials listed for hearing later
OL,19,Fthis month.
