OL,3,CMorrison and Swann settle legal case
OL,5,FBoth lawsuits related to conflicting
OL,6,Fviews on how Mr Swann responded to the
OL,7,Fpandemic in his ministerial capacity.
OL,9,FThe politician, now MP for South
OL,10,FAntrim, sued for slander after Sir Van
OL,11,Fdeclared that he was "very dangerous"
OL,12,Fin front of an audience at Belfast's
OL,13,FEuropa Hotel in June 2021.
OL,15,FIt came after the singer-songwriter's
OL,16,Fgigs at the venue were cancelled due
OL,17,Fto a ban on live music imposed as part
OL,18,Fof coronavirus restrictions.
