OL,6,Fcriticism at Mr Swann, with video
OL,7,Ffootage of the incident subsequently
OL,8,Fgoing viral.
OL,10,FSimilar assertions in a newspaper
OL,11,Finterview and a YouTube video formed
OL,12,Fpart of those proceedings.
OL,14,FIn a separate action, Sir Van sued Mr
OL,15,FSwann and the Department of Health
OL,16,Fover an earlier opinion piece
