OL,5,FThe article appeared in September 2020
OL,6,Fafter the performer announced plans to
OL,7,Frelease anti-lockdown songs and donate
OL,8,Fproceeds to a hardship fund for
OL,9,Fmusicians facing restrictions on live
OL,10,Fperformance.
OL,12,FWith both actions due to get underway
OL,13,Fon September 30, it was announced on
OL,14,FFriday that all proceedings have now
OL,15,Fbeen settled on confidential terms.
OL,17,FIt follows mediation overseen by
OL,18,Fretired senior judge Sir Donnell
OL,19,FDeeney.
