OL,3,CMorrison and Swann settle legal case
OL,5,FNeither Sir Van nor Mr Swann attended
OL,6,Fcourt for the announcement.
OL,8,FBut an agreed statement read out by
OL,9,FDavid Ringland KC, for the politician,
OL,10,Fconfirmed: "Sir Van, while not
OL,11,Fagreeing with a number of the steps
OL,12,Fadopted by government during the Covid
OL,13,Fcrisis, acknowledges that in
OL,14,Fperforming his then role as Minister
OL,15,Ffor Health in Northern Ireland, Mr
OL,16,FSwann acted at all times honestly and
OL,17,Fin good faith and on the advice of
OL,18,Fresponsible officials.
