OL,5,FThe statement went on: "The Department
OL,6,Fof Health acknowledges, with
OL,7,Fhindsight, that any views they may
OL,8,Fhave wished to express about Sir Van's
OL,9,Fsong lyrics might have been more
OL,10,Fappropriately expressed in the usual
OL,11,Fform of media interviews or statements
OL,12,Fprovided to the Northern Ireland
OL,13,Fmedia, rather than providing copy to a
OL,14,FUS rock music magazine.
OL,16,F"The Department of Health welcomes
OL,17,Fthese statements and is glad to have
OL,18,Fassisted in the public interest in the
OL,19,Fresolution of these potentially very
OL,20,Fcostly proceedings."
